javax.telephony.callcontrol

Interface CallControlCallListener

  • All Superinterfaces:
    CallListener, java.util.EventListener
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    CallControlConnectionListener, CallControlTerminalConnectionListener
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    CallControlCallListenerAdapter, CallControlConnectionListenerAdapter, CallControlTerminalConnectionListenerAdapter

    public interface CallControlCallListener
extends CallListener
    The CallControlCallListener interface reports all changes to the Call object. This interface extends the CallListener interfaces. The CallControlConnectionListener and CallControlTerminalConnectionListener interfaces extend this interface.

    This interface supports no additional methods.

    Since:
    1.4
    Version:
    07/01/01 1.4
    See Also:
    Call, CallEvent, CallControlCall, CallControlCallEvent, CallControlConnectionListener, CallControlTerminalConnectionListener
